## Guardrails: High-Risk Tools by Server

When updating Google Workspace server reference pages, add guardrail callouts for:

**google-calendar**: `delete_event`, `modify_event` (can modify attendees)
**google-gmail**: `delete_gmail_filter`, `create_gmail_filter`; NOTE: no `send_gmail_message` tool exists — `draft_gmail_message` only (architectural, not scope-limited)
**google-sheets**: `modify_sheet_values` with `clear_values: true`
**google-drive**: any file deletion tools
**google-docs**: `batch_update_doc`, `find_and_replace_doc` (bulk destructive)

